Summary of modifications relative to the original:
  - Bullet-list auto-formatting in the input area (Enter continues/exits a
    list, Tab / Shift+Tab adjust indentation).
  - Glassmorphic, transparent window styling (backdrop blur).
  - The window stays open on focus loss and is dismissed only with Esc.

